name: Supra-Threshold into VO2 #1
description:
The demands of racing will often require you to be at your limit, but then find some more! Welcome to Supra-Threshold into VO2! 



Today, the focus is on your VO2 work, but we perform this under the stress of starting from a threshold level.
            


            This workout is also available as Video workout by a MyWhoosh coach Si Bradeley
